  "description" : "* Based on a rom-com school manga by http://anidb.net/cr79346 [Agasawa Koucha].\nhttp://anidb.net/ch149504 [Suzuki]`s a high school girl in love, but the guy she`s fallen for is nothing like her! While she`s cheerful, outgoing, and always trying to fit in, her classmate http://anidb.net/ch149503 [Tani Yuusuke] is stoic, quiet, and doesn`t seem to care what people think of him. Will Suzuki be able to overcome her anxieties and ask him out, or will she discover that opposites really don`t attract?\nSource: Viz\nNote: The first episode received an early screening on 5 December 2025 at CCXP in Brazil, on 7 December 2025 at AGF Korea, on 13 December 2025 at Anime Frontier in the United States, on 20 December 2025 at Comic Fiesta in Malaysia, and at a special event on 21 December 2025 at Marunouchi Piccadilly in Tokyo. The regular TV broadcast started on 11 January 2026.",
  "end_date" : "2026-03-29",
